	<h1 class="title">可穿戴市场增长了三倍，但三星被小天才儿童表赶出了前五</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/43366/small/43366.jpg?1430896699" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">王民超 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-05 07:45:38 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18549/medium/18549.jpg?1449216715" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="18549" data-title="《可穿戴市场增长了三倍，但三星被小天才儿童表赶出了前五》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/18549/medium/18549.jpg?1449216715" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/18549" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
